Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.37,0:01:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In my world... there's the sense of \Nsmell, sound, taste and touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These are all I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.53,0:01:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And these are all I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.79,0:01:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.86,0:02:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something in my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:26.91,EP Title BG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2100,0)\p1\blur1}m 0 0 l 950 0 950 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.95,0:02:26.91,EP Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1300,0)\be1}Eye of Fortune, Eye of Misfortune
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.14,0:02:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank god, I've finally come to the main road.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"From all over the ceiling they hang..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:03:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"creatures that resemble black strands of hair"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"When nightfall comes they grow longer"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"And get in your nose so you can't sleep."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.98,0:03:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This story is about mushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Who told you that story?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My father told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to hear some more, mushi-shi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know that I am a mushi-shi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I just had a feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.17,0:03:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, don't make that kind of face...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you listen some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's getting dark, so why not stay around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a guest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... I'm not staying here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, let me carry your luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let me go. Give me back my luggage!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... what story should I talk about next?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your father a mushi-shi as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All your stories sound very real.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Has he retired already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He passed away...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.90,0:04:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Because my eyes weren't helpful...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't see at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I can see very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the {\i1}Ganpuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw the {\i1}Ganpuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be a myth! Where did you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll talk about myself next.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In return, I have a favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.32,0:05:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you go bury these eyes of mine in the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.42,0:05:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Amane!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Amane!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How did your work go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was a mushi-shi, so he was often away from home working, leaving me at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved to listen to the stories about his trips.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've obtained something amazing this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's this mushi called {\i1}Ganpuku,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,which is said to be able to improve your eyesight after you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been said to be only a myth until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I gained possession of \Nthe eyeball of a man who saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Eyeball?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.67,0:06:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, it was taken out after he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that this man was able to see more clearly after seeing the {\i1}Ganpuku
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,for a few years before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And this eyeball remains without decay since his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This may be a clue to finding the {\i1}Ganpuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Amane... I'll make you able to see even if it takes the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise... you just wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wron-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:54.56,Alt,,0,0,0,,Don't open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:06:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What... was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a mushi, hiding in the eyeball!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That could be the {\i1}Ganpuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My father looked around for it in the mountains, but he couldn't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And a month later...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something in my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be... what it's like to be able to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something just got in my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.16,0:08:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be... my dad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Amane?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Amane!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I understood for the first time \Nwhat it meant to be able to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was something that I could never imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.59,0:08:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was a wonderful thing, far beyond my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultramarine blue... Light purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Pink... Orange...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They're wild geese.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, they're very neatly lined up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Saki-chan. And you're Fusa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:09:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you able to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a shiny, flower-like thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyes could see further than any of my friends'.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see you in the bush, Yo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no fun because you find us too quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be "it" anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,As time passed by... I started seeing places that I shouldn't be able to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the hill through the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the mountain range behind that hill...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...and even the sea far beyond that mountain range...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I became able to see them even from the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.94,0:10:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I was fascinated with the unfamiliar\N sceneries and people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But soon after, I started feeling \Ndizzy, and I could hardly walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only when I closed my eyes that peaceful darkness would visit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So I spent most of my time with my eyes closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But after living like that for a while, I started seeing something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.01,0:10:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.64,0:10:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouchhh... There was a sudden gust of wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was that I just saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When I closed my eyes, I would see the future and the past of people around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And soon people started coming over to ask me to read their future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything I saw became true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumors that I was a clairvoyant spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.27,0:11:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And even people from neighboring \Nvillages came to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Next summer, you'll fall into a river and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't go near the river for any reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.91,0:11:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But even though I warned people, I was never able to change what I saw in my visions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And eventually, the people who came to see me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,only asked about thieves or other \Nunsavory types of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:12:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Although my eyes proved useful for people, all my friends left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,People must think clairvoyants are creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I can see what's going to happen, nothing changes after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped seeing people's past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But... then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah?! What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can see outside through my eyelids...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Amane, I'm going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Amane? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I see your future and the scenery \Noutside at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel dizzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:13:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry... I'll get used to it soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back in three days. Take it easy, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But father never came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I went to the mountains every single day
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to look for my father using my clairvoyance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And one day, I finally saw my father lying on the bottom of a ravine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I started my journey \Nin order to grieve for my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Along the way, I told the stories\N I heard from my father
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,while playing my lute \Nfor money during the journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And after I finally arrived at \Nthe site of my father's remains,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I no longer wanted to return to the village to which my father would never return.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:14:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, I've been playing the lute\N on the street for a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And as time passed, I could see more and more through my eyelids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.51,0:14:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There was nothing to obstruct my view.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was tough for me to stand\N the light during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was still one thing that I couldn't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That was... my own future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I was able to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you would pass through this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the fact that I would have to ask you to do something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...that was all foreseen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And you want me to tear out your clairvoyant eyes and bury them in the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.34,0:14:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to ask someone else to do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've done it myself long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,These eyes once brought me so much joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,so I managed to live with them until now, even though I hated them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this pair of eyes soon\N won't belong to me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the {\i1}Ganpuku{\i0} that I saw,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll get out of my eyeballs and go under ground
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to wait for the next pair of new eyeballs to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't want anyone to have\N the same experience as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want you to bury\N my eyes deep in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.02,0:15:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that you saw all that in your visions?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd understand if you were \Nasking me to cure your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't say for sure there is no way to cure your eyes, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I just told you... that the things I saw can't be changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The things my eyes see are something that exist in a far, unreachable place
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and are already destined to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't swallow everything you've told me tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you write to your friend for help, you won't get a useful reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.27,0:16:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so eager to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because you lost your left eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see that with your clairvoyance, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In your case, I can't see anything, because your childhood is pitch black.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My oldest memory is of walking alone in some dark, unknown place when I was about ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.47,0:17:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept groping about in the dark, \Nand then the moon came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after this pure-white, illusionary moon set,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,what rose was yet another moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,After walking for along time in that place,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally came to a place where the sun rises.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I still remember well how I appreciated\N the sunlight back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you scared of losing light forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But a world with only light is just as scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see everything but you can't change anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.09,0:17:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you can't see anything but you can live freely...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one do you think is more fortunate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:18:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that living in the darkness, \Nremembering the light, is not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.65,0:18:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I just... saw it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How far did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it to the moment that the lives of my eyeballs come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her eyes were not able to see\N through her eyelids before...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She could only see other people's futures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But now she can see through her eyelids and is able to see her own future...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:19:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does that mean that she is becoming another person to her eyeballs?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A mushi that takes shelter in the eye\N after someone looks at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It changes the eyeballs into something else that can live on after the person dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And soon it will take over the eyeballs completely and then leave the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the time for it to leave must be close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is still no reply...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Things that are already destined to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? I can't see behind the ceiling...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can see... normally...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah? But... my eyeballs are moving by themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on! I'll give you a painkiller.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Even... without... eyeballs...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.43,0:20:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...tears still flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:21:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How far did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it to the moment that the lives of my eyeballs come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,After the eyeballs leave my eyes, \Nthey are buried in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,After a while, they reveal \Nthemselves from the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.65,0:21:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and a beast walks toward them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful flowers are reflected \Nupon the eyes of the beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And as they are slowly being absorbed into the eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,then everything goes dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have a reply from your friend by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:44.40,Caligraph,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...research...\N...no known treatments...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.19,0:21:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going back to your village?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.59,0:22:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to live by myself for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.69,0:22:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad that I don't know what will happen anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.69,0:22:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you happen to see me, please say hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.38,0:22:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be a much better lute player by then.
